data.description: BACK ON MARKET AT NO FAULT OF SELLER! Discover your dream home in the coveted Hyde Park neighborhood of Cumming, GA! This enchanting 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem is nestled on a vast 1-acre lot, providing an idyllic blend of privacy and comfort. Enjoy peace of mind with a ONE-YEAR home warranty, a brand-new water heater, and a recently serviced septic system. Step inside to experience the warmth and charm of this lovingly maintained property. Each spacious bedroom offers a serene sanctuary for rest, while the 2.5 well-designed bathrooms cater to your daily necessities. The versatile finished basement can be transformed into a game room, home office, or fitness area. Embrace outdoor living in the expansive, fenced-in backyard - the perfect setting for family gatherings, barbecues, or quiet moments amidst nature. The air-conditioned, insulated work shed, complete with power, caters to hobbyists and DIY enthusiasts alike. The attached two-car garage ensures secure parking and ample storage. As a resident of the prestigious Hyde Park community, you''ll enjoy easy access to local amenities, top-rated schools, and scenic parks. Don''t let this incredible opportunity slip away - schedule a private showing today and envision your new life in this exceptional home! Bonus: The 65'' Roku TV & sound system are included.
